Update ALL enchanter Spells that are enchant on a weapon has gotten a revamp
if you have a *6 of the spell for Minor-Major of Acc, Puissance, Fort It will be a 1 time cast to fully filly up that weapon or armour
anything lower then *6 follows the same rules as before multiple casts to fill it up


